commits.content:
[package]
name = "extraction"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]
tokio = { version = "1.28.0", features = ["full"] }
serde = { version = "1.0.204", features = ["derive"] }
serde_json = "1.0.68"
dotenvy = "=0.15.7"
config = "0.14.0"
chrono = { version = "0.4.38", features = ["serde"] }
once_cell = "1.19.0"
uuid = { version = "1.8.0", features = ["v4", "v5"] }
actix-web = "4.8.0"
pdf = "0.9.0"
lopdf = "0.33.0"
humantime = "2.1.0"
reqwest = { version = "0.12.5",  features = ["blocking", "json", "multipart"]}
actix-multipart = "0.7.2"   
tempfile = "3.10.1"
quick-xml = "0.36.1"
futures-util = "0.3.30"
env_logger = "0.11.5"
tempdir = "0.3.7"

[[bin]]
name = "main"
path = "src/main.rs"

[[bin]]
name = "load_file_ids"
path = "src/bin/load_file_ids.rs"

[[bin]]
name = "load_metadata_trieve"
path = "src/bin/load_metadata_trieve.rs"

[[bin]]
name = "load_pagination"
path = "src/bin/load_pagination.rs"

[[bin]]
name = "xml"
path = "src/bin/xml.rs"

[[bin]]
name = "extraction"
path = "src/bin/extraction/main.rs"
